data.description: If you are looking for a home that has been impeccably cared for, this is the one! This adorable ranch in the Hickory school district is completely move-in ready. From the curb appeal in the front to the in-ground swimming pool in the back yard, it just makes you want to stay home and enjoy your space. Two fully electrified sheds for plenty of storage in the fully fenced yard and one detached garage for motorcycle and pool equipment.
